{"tid":1614231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國手足致Pelosi書","createTime":"2019-10-02T17:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T19:48:12.000Z","uid":79046,"like":169,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"aa02d1bb4c15d1d21b2449e9d310492370c61bb8","tid":1614231,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:23:31.000Z","msg":"有美國手足琴日見咗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>美國眾議員議長Speaker Pelosi</strong></span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遞咗幾封信上去，包括之前收集左大家既意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n篇幅有限，未必所有意見都寫咗落去，請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感謝每一位香港人嘅付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我開咗個drive放左果幾封信上去，以下係drive link<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1Q6QW9Xh_8Ihrw74oHJJXQ5KrER3kOf5s?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1Q6QW9Xh_8Ihrw74oHJJXQ5KrER3kOf5s%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7BjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=d6aab5c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1Q6QW9Xh_8Ihrw74oHJJXQ5KrER3kOf5s?usp=sharing</a><br />\n文宣同啱用嘅手足們<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請隨便取用！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前收集左大家既意見， 會再諗下點好好運用，手足有咩建議可以留言講下<br />\nE.g. 開個網站放大家嘅經歷、堅持同訴求上去？"},{"pid":"8dff056f26d0f2f3999894ff760367908ff18283","tid":1614231,"uid":8762,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:25:18.000Z","msg":"感謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12491dc723a306a090f7e632a355e5be0d2ffe7b","tid":1614231,"uid":19557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:27:52.000Z","msg":"感謝美國手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb93bf2c5153f499195c9a4b346140e31bfe356c","tid":1614231,"uid":9049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:33:38.000Z","msg":"Push推 <br />\nSignature簽名檔：保衛家園，對抗極權<br />\n「反極權運動」守護香港，深層改革<br />\n<br />\n抗爭轉型及進化建議：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">重要目標：</span></strong>11月24號區議會選舉<br />\n和平勇武後勤文宣議員：各司其職<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">強調：</span></strong>愛港市民、美國制裁、親北京賣港賊、暴政殘害人民、公平公正選舉<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">防範：</span></strong>掌心雷、利誘淺黃淺藍市民、抹黑<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">流水式示威：</span></strong>警察舉旗咪去另一個地方示威，香港咁多地方可以去，佢想捉你，你咪話走緊囉，太多人行得慢好正常，合情合理合法！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">適當武力/自衛反擊：</span></strong>合情又合理！<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>游擊戰？：</strong></span>對抗黑社會/恐怖分子<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">創意活動：</span></strong>唱歌比賽？跑步大叫？商場罷買<br />\n諗到再加<br />\n<br />\n公平、自由、民主、公義、人權<span style=\"color: gold;\">得來不易</span><br />\n漫長的道路上需要<span style=\"color: gold;\">你支持我，我扶持你</span><br />\n有時惘然若失，但我們也要<span style=\"color: gold;\">自信往前邁步</span><br />\n有咩嘢唔想失去，就努力<span style=\"color: gold;\">捍衛</span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\">守護</span><br />\n現在就用自己雙手實踐夢想，<span style=\"color: gold;\">迎接未來</span><br />\n<br />\n短期目標：改善抗爭能力，提升身份認同<br />\n建議：各有各做，best effort <br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化民主陣營勢力<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、傳播思想、滲透內部<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公務員</span></strong>：小隱於野，中隱於市，大隱於朝<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和勇合一</strong></span>：1.合法之下，最大勇武<br />\n                     2. 做任何事，永不被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n只要爭取民主團火未熄，還是有機會達成<br />\n衛城革命,生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡,打倒腐敗<br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<strong><em>升級技能/能力值/level</em></strong>：1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.和勇合一精神4.批判性思考5.精通專業技能6.低消費、高儲蓄<br />\n<strong><em>每日任務：</em></strong>1.幫襯良心商店、抵制送中商戶2.開AC玩國際戰線 (Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)3.多發佈正面資訊、冷處理負面POST4.十點咆哮發泄5.思考完就take action<br />\n<strong><em>每星期任務</em></strong>：1. 罷買日2. 教育家中兩老3. 去連儂牆幫手4.參加一樣民主活動5. 諗下點樣爭取民主<br />\n<strong><em>每月任務</em></strong>：1. 換美金，走資2. 陪審員/派傳單/放映會/各有各做<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7BjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=3c80ecb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7BjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=6aed34a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7BjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=44df4506\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.10.02<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">要記住極權如何打壓香港示威：</span></strong><br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨、新華社、環球時報、人民日報<br />\n2.誤導：送中條例、說謊、黃色object等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n10.扮好人/扮對話：「江山易改本性難移」<br />\n11.警察濫權、濫捕、暴力執法、恐嚇<br />\n12.利用親中人士發表「假」權威言論<br />\n諗到再加</span><br />\nVictory at all costs, victory in spite of all terror, victory however long and hard the road may be; for without victory, there is no survival.<br />\nWinston Churchill"},{"pid":"553bbbfc06a68079f66b65cb06fc51c01c4caec3","tid":1614231,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:40:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef128b0c071ac77c37248b364046f0ba31e24b6a","tid":1614231,"uid":113587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8044e6f488fa6055eb750b9158319a22090991a1","tid":1614231,"uid":242737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:57:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"752a5053e8bea4f187893e6dffa4a466808ab2a7","tid":1614231,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:58:05.000Z","msg":"感謝美國手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6d155a14ada791f7544a578751d2c5b6365cc0","tid":1614231,"uid":273807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91eeca48ef60c2299c7e29512911120099525002","tid":1614231,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:06:32.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif